{"tid":280352,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本d廢老都幾無禮貌","createTime":"2017-06-12T04:26:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T04:24:53.000Z","uid":51200,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb9ffb054413b7df072bcf8069cb9f02a317bdad","tid":280352,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:26:54.000Z","msg":"正話上機前Check機票，<br />\n有幾個亞洲廢老(有啊伯啊嬸)捐黎捐去打尖，<br />\n原本以為係大陸人或者香港廢老，點知講日文既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最撚柒既係，打完把鬼婆鬼佬尖，<br />\n到真係Check passport 既時候，個staff先話班友排錯隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後一個日本啊伯就捐返欄杆出去，<br />\n其餘幾個啊嬸竟然逆方向行出去,搞到成班人塞住阻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到我後面班鬼婆同鬼佬不停望住幾條日本廢老恥笑定點，<br />\n真係好丟架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688389066a7ed976668ff81d3abe43b1ead92270","tid":280352,"uid":18587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:47:02.000Z","msg":"廢老無分國界的"},{"pid":"b53d95d976011bf345c177df37079ccfe5fdc523","tid":280352,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T19:50:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢老無分國界的</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class